Ad Sales & Marketing Executive
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 08:08:36
Ref. JB2995512
Job Description
- Ad space selling for print and online publications.
- Sourcing new potential clients and updating CRM
- Regular client correspondence and follow ups with clients and media agencies
- Sending out deadline reminders
- Ad material collection, co-ordination with design team and getting approvals on artworks from clients.
- Helping and co-ordinating with circulation managers to ensure proper targetting for circulation and distribution.
Skills
- Should have ad space selling experience in Dubai for atleast 1 year.
- With good relations with all media buying agencies across UAE.
- Experience is events management would be a definite plus.
- Excellent Social, administrative and correspondence skills
- Good organisational skills
- Good communication skills in English
- Arabic language would be an added advantage
